quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  75,31,"Enti (boniayεni no) annye (Qur’aan) anni, εna wannfrε Nyame nso"
  75,32,Na mmom obuu no atorͻsεm danee n’akyi demaae
  75,33,Afei ͻde ahomasoͻ kunkon kͻͻ n’abusuafoͻ hͻ
  75,34,Due nka wo. Enti Due
  75,35,"Due nka wo bio, Enti Due"
  75,36,Enti onipa dwen sε yε’bεgyae no kwa
  75,37,"Na ͻnnyε nkwa-boaa a, efiri ahobae a, ehwie anaa epue ba no mu"
  75,38,"Ansa na ͻreyε mogya-toa, εna (Nyankopͻn) bͻͻ (no) yεε (no) pεpεεpε"
  75,39,"Ɛna Ͻyεε no mmienu, ͻbarima ne ͻbaa"
  75,40,"Enti (Nyankopͻn a, ͻnam anwanwa kwan a yakyerε yi so bͻͻ onipa no), Onni tumi sε Ɔbenyane owufoͻ aba nkwa mu (bio)"